{"tid":1782083,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"快D去台灣着草啊","createTime":"2019-12-13T15:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T16:31:48.000Z","uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"928bd20aee7484329bc3b4ee6af16d948713a358","tid":1782083,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191213/mobile/bkn-20191213225920591-1213_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191213%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191213225920591-1213_00822_001.html&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=7b8bd227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191213/mobile/bkn-20191213225920591-1213_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一名70歲老翁羅長清，上月13日早上約11時52分，途經上水龍運街北區大會堂外馬路時，被人投擲硬物擊中頭部受傷，翌日傷重死亡，當日亦有多名市民被掟中受傷。警方於本周二(10日)在其Facebook專頁貼文，指懸紅80萬元欲緝拿真兇。據了解，新界北警區重案組探員今日(13日)拘捕5人(15至18歲)，涉嫌當日投擲雜物，掟傷在場其他市民。"},{"pid":"3f99482919a13241a936e1584840fe15bba420a2","tid":1782083,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7785f98a36cae1fe4588a0ae995e4aacd0b44939","tid":1782083,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cda02e6055921cd1a14b50f968aca893d81b70b","tid":1782083,"uid":263406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:54:31.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借一借位宣傳<br />\n［行動post]入黎睇！一個真正經濟攬炒既平安夜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f5728e046c10294c80ea753f023098c814402f18","tid":1782083,"uid":3066